-- Newark Airport Terminal A Closed Because of Suspicious Package, WABC Says
-- B y   H e a t h e r   B u r k e
-- 2010-12-20T13:16:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-20/newark-airport-terminal-a-closed-because-of-suspicious-package-wabc-says.html
Newark Liberty International
Airport’s Terminal A was shut down because of a suspicious
package, WABC reported on its website.  Authorities may be looking into a possible bomb at AMR
Corp.’s American Airlines counter, WABC said, without saying
where it got the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
